parameters:
Lutecia: "Here... Kusechirei should be here... That man named Shif must
have gone ahead..."
Kru: "So what... I mean... it's enough already"

Lutecia: "Kusechirei is trying to incarnate using Umi's body and revive.
And then this world will end..."

Lutecia: "I will stop it... I can't let everything become Kusechirei's
offspring, and all life's mother become Kusechirei... That's not
acceptable"
Kru: "...I'll go... I don't really understand, but... I'll go"
Kru: "No... it's just a little headache... I'm fine... I can go on..."
